name: Ten Hands and a Fortune
description: In various regions, fish is interpreted as a symbol of good luck, I drew a fish with ten hands to represent my idea of ​​human efforts to fulfill their needs and do something to make their dreams come true. I believe that luck is relative, can come from anywhere and cannot be separated from human efforts to make all things that were originally abstract become real. So everyone who tries will surely find his luck at the right time.
